divs: Sighting DetailsDriving to work a bright object caught my eye a few inches above the treeline but definitely a couple miles away. Tried to follow it with eyes while staying on road but lost visual after a minute, due to treeline. About 1 minute later I noticed a pair of fighter jets in formation, flying at very low altitude, and they appeared to zoom in the direction of where the UFO had appeared to be heading (towards the ocean).
